sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant AI as AI App
    participant SM as Supermemory API
    participant IDX as Memory Index

    U->>AI: "I just moved to San Francisco"
    AI->>AI: addMemory = always?
    AI->>SM: POST /v4/conversations\n[messages array]
    SM->>SM: Extract facts from text
    Note over SM: "User lives in San Francisco"\n"Used to live in NYC"
    SM->>SM: Check existing memory
    Note over SM: Found old: "Lives in NYC"
    SM->>SM: Conflict resolution
    Note over SM: NEW replaces OLD
    SM->>IDX: Save updated fact\n+ semantic embedding
    SM->>AI: 200 OK
    AI->>U: Response (no delay)

    Note over IDX: Static: "Lives in SF"\nDynamic: "Recently moved"
